snippet.title: Disgaea 6: Defiance of Destiny - Release Date Announcement - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Disgaea 6: Defiance of Destiny has all the madness, chaos, and Netherworldly action you can handle... plus more! Coming June 29, 2021 to Nintendo Switch!

Learn more: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/disgaea-6-defiance-of-destiny-switch/
